Feature: Payment Flow
As a user
In order to purchase paid content
I would like to be able to enter credit card information or pay via my existing PayPal account

Scenario: User is able to review the content being purchased
Scenario: User is able to review what rights they will be awarded by purchasing this content
Scenario: User is able to select via radio button whether to pay by Credit Card or PayPal Express
Scenario: User is able to make a payment via credit card
Scenario: User is able to make a payment via PayPal Express
